assert is used to validate invariants.
require is used to validate user inputs.

assert is triggered if:
    out of index
    division by zero
    byteshifting by a negative amount.
    convert a value too big or negative to enum.
    zero initialized variable of type function type.

require is triggered if:
    where the condition evaluates to false.
    function call via message call but doesn't finish properly.
    external function call to a contract not containing any code.
    your contract receiving ether without payable.
    your contract receives ether at a getter function.
    address.transfer() fails